1
00:01:25,450 --> 00:01:29,940
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,740 --> 00:01:33,840
[Episode 32]

3
00:01:58,539 --> 00:02:01,360
I, daughter-in-law Shen Wan,
pay my respects to you, Father.

4
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,229
Chief General.

5
00:02:02,810 --> 00:02:03,960
I, Bai Feng,

6
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,970
kowtow to you.

7
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,450
His Majesty has decreed

8
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,009
that tomorrow at 6 a.m.,

9
00:02:18,130 --> 00:02:20,060
we shall leave the city for burial.

10
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,009
No wake

11
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:22,250
and no mourning?

12
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,680
His Majesty said that

13
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:27,320
Father died at the hands of
the nomadic enemies,

14
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:30,450
so holding a wake or mourning rite
would be a breach of propriety.

15
00:02:30,450 --> 00:02:33,050
How could His Majesty
speak such absurd words?

16
00:02:47,690 --> 00:02:48,370
Wan.

17
00:02:52,130 --> 00:02:53,010
Help me.

18
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:04,640
Father.

19
00:03:05,250 --> 00:03:06,290
This is Shen Wan,

20
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,840
the woman I've chosen as my wife.

21
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,970
If you suffered any injustice,

22
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:13,130
the two of us will definitely
seek justice for you.

23
00:03:13,130 --> 00:03:14,640
Father, you've tragically passed away,

24
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:15,850
and I, Shen Wan, your daughter-in-law,

25
00:03:15,850 --> 00:03:17,500
have to perform an autopsy.

26
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,970
If there's any offense,

27
00:03:18,970 --> 00:03:20,500
please forgive me, Father.

28
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:24,930
Wan.

29
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,480
We only have six hours.

30
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,420
Time is tight.

31
00:03:27,590 --> 00:03:28,380
Just tell me

32
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,930
what you need me to examine.

33
00:03:30,250 --> 00:03:31,290
I want to know

34
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:34,360
whether Father was truly killed
by the nomadic enemies.

35
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:34,920
Okay.

36
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,320
I'll focus on examining the murder weapon

37
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,780
and the method of killing.

38
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,800
There're a total of

39
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,329
17 wounds on Father's body.

40
00:04:07,079 --> 00:04:08,290
There are seven abrasions

41
00:04:08,290 --> 00:04:09,079
on the left shoulder,

42
00:04:09,079 --> 00:04:10,120
back,

43
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:11,290
right wrist bone,

44
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:12,570
and right calf.

45
00:04:12,570 --> 00:04:13,730
There're four impact or collision injuries

46
00:04:13,730 --> 00:04:15,570
on the chest and abdomen.

47
00:04:15,930 --> 00:04:17,420
The fatal wound is on the chest,

48
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:19,820
caused by a sharp arrow
piercing the heart.

49
00:04:19,890 --> 00:04:21,420
Where was Father attacked?

50
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,970
Father was attacked
while on a border patrol,

51
00:04:23,970 --> 00:04:25,900
during a brief rest at a posthouse.

52
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,800
These are the grain husks I found

53
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,930
in Father's hair, used for horse feeding.

54
00:04:32,930 --> 00:04:34,080
Father's limbs

55
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,960
all have groove-shaped blood stains.

56
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,610
It appears that during the fight,

57
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:38,960
someone threw bran in his face,

58
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,050
blocking his vision,

59
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:41,400
then bound his limbs.

60
00:04:41,810 --> 00:04:43,159
This method of restraint

61
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:45,130
could even control a bull.

62
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:52,480
At that time,
Father was preparing to depart

63
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:56,740
and had sent his personal guard, Fan Xin,
to lead his horse from the backyard.

64
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:14,400
Father practiced martial arts continuously
throughout his life.

65
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,840
If it weren't for such a vicious method,

66
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,760
it would have been impossible
to subdue him.

67
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,960
Since the killer wanted to kill Father,

68
00:07:20,050 --> 00:07:22,610
they could have simply used
a rope to choke him.

69
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:24,200
Why go to the trouble

70
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,370
to bind his limbs?

71
00:07:27,450 --> 00:07:28,200
Unless...

72
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,580
Why is this arrow wound

73
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:43,560
different from ordinary ones?

74
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,480
It's a four-edged arrow.

75
00:07:49,010 --> 00:07:50,810
This is a weapon unique to
the nomadic enemies.

76
00:07:50,810 --> 00:07:51,760
Since the arrowhead is heavy

77
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,760
and has barbs,

78
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:54,680
regular bows cannot shoot them.

79
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:57,880
This kind of arrow can only be fired
using a hand crossbow.

80
00:07:58,450 --> 00:07:59,960
Since they had already bound

81
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,440
Father's limbs with rope,

82
00:08:02,210 --> 00:08:03,550
wouldn't using a hand crossbow

83
00:08:03,550 --> 00:08:05,080
seem too deliberate?

84
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:08,940
Could it be that

85
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,720
they wanted to...

86
00:08:41,970 --> 00:08:43,640
They wanted to trap Father

87
00:08:44,590 --> 00:08:47,130
and then create the illusion of
him being shot through the heart.

88
00:08:47,130 --> 00:08:49,159
How could they act so boldly

89
00:08:49,539 --> 00:08:51,000
without anyone noticing?

90
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,679
By the time Fan Xin arrived,

91
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:55,610
Father had already been shot
with the arrow and died.

92
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:08,100
G-General...

93
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,130
General!

94
00:09:14,730 --> 00:09:15,930
When the killer left,

95
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:16,890
they deliberately took the ropes

96
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,750
that bound Father's limbs

97
00:09:18,850 --> 00:09:20,370
and left behind the four-edged arrow,

98
00:09:20,370 --> 00:09:21,680
as if to make it known that

99
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:23,450
it was done by the nomadic enemies.

100
00:09:23,450 --> 00:09:25,150
Was that a provocation against
the Shuoxi Army?

101
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:27,040
The nomadic enemies have harbored a deep
and long-standing hatred for Father,

102
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,760
and they reward deeds with decapitation.

103
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:30,320
If it was really a provocation
from the nomadic enemies,

104
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,370
Father's body would certainly
not be intact.

105
00:09:32,370 --> 00:09:33,850
If it wasn't the nomadic enemies,

106
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:35,320
then someone's trying to frame them.

107
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,490
The killer must be familiar with
the nomadic enemies' weapons.

108
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:39,400
And they're also familiar with Father's
border patrol routes.

109
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,440
If that's the case,

110
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:43,210
those within the Shuoxi Army
are the most suspicious.

111
00:09:43,210 --> 00:09:44,730
It's time to meet Fan Xin.

112
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,970
When you passed through the posthouse,

113
00:09:47,970 --> 00:09:50,230
did you notice any traces of foreigners?

114
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,040
No.

115
00:09:51,490 --> 00:09:53,800
After the Crown Prince of Beidai
had an accident,

116
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:57,260
His Lordship had already ordered
strict border inspections.

117
00:09:57,490 --> 00:09:58,250
Then, General,

118
00:09:58,250 --> 00:10:00,560
did you get a good look at
the assassinator's appearance?

119
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,250
No.

120
00:10:01,970 --> 00:10:02,920
By the time I arrived,

121
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:04,180
the villains had already fled,

122
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:06,640
and His Lordship and our men
were already...

123
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:09,330
General Fan, you've followed His Lordship
for many years.

124
00:10:09,330 --> 00:10:11,760
Have you ever seen the nomadic enemies
use rope formations

125
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,250
to encircle our soldiers and civilians?

126
00:10:13,250 --> 00:10:14,640
Rope formations?

127
00:10:15,850 --> 00:10:17,680
How does Your Highness know about this?

128
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:19,010
What do you mean by that?

129
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:21,160
Young Marshal, you may not know this,

130
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:22,560
but after you entered the capital,

131
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,960
His Lordship ordered the Tianshu Camp

132
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,280
to adapt our Zhou's meteor hammer

133
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:26,630
into a rope formation,

134
00:10:26,890 --> 00:10:29,010
specifically to force
the nomadic enemies to surrender.

135
00:10:29,010 --> 00:10:30,470
Besides the Tianshu Camp,

136
00:10:30,810 --> 00:10:32,250
who else knows about this formation?

137
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:33,090
No one.

138
00:10:33,730 --> 00:10:35,130
Such a confidential formation

139
00:10:35,130 --> 00:10:36,970
is known only to His Lordship

140
00:10:37,590 --> 00:10:39,650
and the soldiers of the Tianshu Camp.

141
00:10:40,970 --> 00:10:42,000
The Tianshu Camp?

142
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,340
The Tianshu Camp

143
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:45,850
is a special unit within the Shuoxi Army

144
00:10:45,850 --> 00:10:48,250
dedicated to assassinating enemy generals.

145
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:49,110
Could it be that

146
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:51,370
there really is a traitor
within the Shuoxi Army?

147
00:10:51,370 --> 00:10:54,830
I never thought Father would die
at the hands of our own people.

148
00:11:22,210 --> 00:11:22,930
Father.

149
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:25,180
I, Shen Wan, hereby swear that

150
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:27,640
no matter who killed you,

151
00:11:28,090 --> 00:11:29,890
I will do everything in my power,

152
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,590
together with Yan Chi,

153
00:11:31,970 --> 00:11:33,640
to avenge your bloodshed.

154
00:11:48,330 --> 00:11:50,050
[Funing Palace]

155
00:11:51,490 --> 00:11:53,440
I want to see my son.

156
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,040
Your Majesty, you cannot go!

157
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:56,850
I want to see him.

158
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:58,640
I beg Your Majesty
to prioritize your health above all else!

159
00:11:58,640 --> 00:11:59,840
My son...

160
00:11:59,970 --> 00:12:01,890
His Majesty arrives!

161
00:12:01,890 --> 00:12:04,220
-I need to see him.
-Mother!

162
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:06,940
Mother, what are you trying to do?

163
00:12:06,970 --> 00:12:10,090
-What is this for, Mother?
-I want to see my son.

164
00:12:12,250 --> 00:12:13,730
Mother...

165
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:15,880
All of you, step back.

166
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:17,160
Quick.

167
00:12:17,850 --> 00:12:18,580
Mother.

168
00:12:18,730 --> 00:12:20,130
Please listen to me.

169
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:21,640
Once you've

170
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:23,520
fully recovered,

171
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:24,400
I'll

172
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:26,040
personally accompany you

173
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:28,400
to pay respects to Lin.
How does that sound?

174
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:29,890
By then,

175
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:35,040
I will only be able to see a tomb.

176
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:37,280
Don't stop me. Let me go!

177
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:39,130
Mother. Mother.

178
00:12:39,130 --> 00:12:41,760
I had no choice in this matter, either.

179
00:12:42,210 --> 00:12:44,890
I am not only his elder brother,

180
00:12:45,250 --> 00:12:47,210
but also the ruler of this country.

181
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:50,920
I have to prioritize state affairs.

182
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,670
What does that matter?

183
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:55,850
Lin was

184
00:12:56,490 --> 00:12:58,250
always loyal to you.

185
00:12:58,970 --> 00:13:00,670
Since your coronation,

186
00:13:01,230 --> 00:13:04,330
he guarded the border for over 20 years.

187
00:13:04,890 --> 00:13:06,810
Without your orders,

188
00:13:07,090 --> 00:13:10,120
he would never step a foot
beyond the Shuoxi border,

189
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:13,890
yet you always treated him
as a grave threat.

190
00:13:13,890 --> 00:13:15,970
Even after his death,

191
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:19,980
you were stingy
in handling his funeral matters.

192
00:13:20,250 --> 00:13:22,370
What kind of emperor are you?

193
00:13:23,210 --> 00:13:25,630
What kind of elder brother are you?

194
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:28,640
Mother, it's all my fault

195
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:31,640
for making you so heartbroken.

196
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,250
But Mother,

197
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:36,800
Lin's sudden death

198
00:13:37,370 --> 00:13:41,680
will surely cause turmoil
at the border and in court.

199
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,210
I

200
00:13:43,370 --> 00:13:46,520
have no choice but
to simplify the funeral ceremonies.

201
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,280
It's also to stabilize the border

202
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,880
and ensure a smooth transfer

203
00:13:50,130 --> 00:13:53,370
of the Shuoxi Army's command.

204
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:55,920
For the sake of your court,

205
00:13:57,370 --> 00:13:59,890
I've compromised again and again.

206
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:03,210
Am I supposed to compromise to the point
where I can't even

207
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:04,970
see my son one last time?

208
00:14:06,130 --> 00:14:07,620
I might as well

209
00:14:07,970 --> 00:14:09,640
not serve as Empress Dowager anymore!

210
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:11,130
Mother!

211
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:16,350
Is it that

212
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:18,440
you only

213
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:21,040
care about Lin?

214
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:28,180
Then what about me?

215
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:31,090
I am

216
00:14:33,010 --> 00:14:34,230
also your

217
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:38,130
own flesh and blood.

218
00:15:15,970 --> 00:15:17,370
Are you saying the victim

219
00:15:17,370 --> 00:15:19,230
was Prince Jin's personal guard,

220
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:20,640
Song Xiwen?

221
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:23,890
A man who should have been imprisoned
in the Imperial Punishment Department

222
00:15:23,890 --> 00:15:26,620
ended up dead
at the Disgraced Prince's mansion.

223
00:15:27,370 --> 00:15:28,290
This matter

224
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:30,160
is indeed suspicious.

225
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:33,680
Your Majesty.

226
00:15:34,090 --> 00:15:36,130
The case of the Disgraced Prince
has long been concluded.

227
00:15:36,130 --> 00:15:38,470
Even if the deceased is truly Song Xiwen,

228
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:41,520
he's merely a guard of no consequence
to the bigger picture,

229
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:44,160
and escaping prison
is itself a capital offense.

230
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,800
If we investigate this case further,

231
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:48,250
stirring up settled matters

232
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:49,370
and muddying clear waters,

233
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,560
it would be unwise.

234
00:15:55,010 --> 00:15:55,810
Your Majesty.

235
00:15:56,090 --> 00:15:58,250
Marquis of Zhongyong makes a valid point.

236
00:15:58,250 --> 00:16:01,440
However, there are many rumors about
the male corpse found

237
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,160
at the Disgraced Prince's mansion,
and if we neglect to investigate,

238
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:04,680
I fear it will only
increase public suspicion

239
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:08,480
and create new complications over
the Disgraced Prince's old case.

240
00:16:15,520 --> 00:16:16,520
Li Muyun.

241
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:19,860
Yes, Your Majesty.

242
00:16:20,130 --> 00:16:23,010
This case was to be supervised
by your Supreme Court.

243
00:16:23,010 --> 00:16:25,660
How do you plan to handle it?

244
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:26,890
Your Majesty.

245
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,110
I believe

246
00:16:28,370 --> 00:16:29,970
this case must be investigated.

247
00:16:29,970 --> 00:16:32,370
For the reputation of the Supreme Court,
it must be investigated.

248
00:16:32,370 --> 00:16:34,850
For the peace of the court,
it must be investigated even more.

249
00:16:34,850 --> 00:16:37,210
I am willing to thoroughly
investigate this case,

250
00:16:37,210 --> 00:16:38,400
so as to provide Your Majesty,

251
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:39,490
the court,

252
00:16:40,040 --> 00:16:42,770
and the people of Zhou
with a proper explanation.

253
00:16:44,210 --> 00:16:45,950
Since Prince Rui has recently passed away,

254
00:16:45,950 --> 00:16:48,710
his son, Yan Chi, is in mourning.

255
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:51,130
Thus, this case shall be

256
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:53,680
handled by Prince Cheng, Yan Qi,
as the acting official.

257
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:57,160
The Supreme Court shall assist
Prince Cheng in supervising this case.

258
00:16:57,160 --> 00:16:59,090
-Yes, Father.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

259
00:17:05,850 --> 00:17:09,260
[Funing Palace]

260
00:17:20,849 --> 00:17:22,480
Why have you returned so soon?

261
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:24,079
Is everything taken care of?

262
00:17:24,369 --> 00:17:26,230
Father has been properly buried.

263
00:17:26,890 --> 00:17:28,400
Given the current situation,

264
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,530
the sooner I return,

265
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,530
the more at ease His Majesty will be.

266
00:17:31,530 --> 00:17:32,460
Do you know that

267
00:17:32,810 --> 00:17:34,480
His Majesty has assigned Song Xiwen's case

268
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,770
to Prince Cheng?

269
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:36,800
I do.

270
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:39,960
Wan.

271
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:43,480
If I lose my position
at the Ministry of Justice

272
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,210
and fail to inherit the throne,

273
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,770
would you still be willing to marry me?

274
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,480
I could open a medical clinic

275
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:53,530
and support you quite comfortably.

276
00:17:56,770 --> 00:17:57,630
Yan Chi.

