546
00:33:20,610 --> 00:33:21,540
Shut your mouth!

547
00:33:22,330 --> 00:33:23,440
Song Xiwen's case

548
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,960
has nothing to do with us.

549
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,680
Let them investigate all they want.

550
00:33:27,850 --> 00:33:29,400
It won't implicate us.

551
00:33:30,330 --> 00:33:33,190
Just focus on being the Crown Prince
without worry.

552
00:33:42,810 --> 00:33:43,610
Father.

553
00:33:44,330 --> 00:33:46,180
The attendants responsible for
guarding Song Xiwen

554
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,160
all refused to confess.

555
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,920
I had no choice but
to use severe punishment,

556
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:50,650
and finally one attendant confessed.

557
00:33:50,650 --> 00:33:52,380
The one who took Song Xiwen away

558
00:33:53,610 --> 00:33:55,530
was the Empress's personal attendant,

559
00:33:55,530 --> 00:33:56,240
Wan Xi.

560
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:08,760
Then where is

561
00:34:09,160 --> 00:34:11,090
Wan Xi's confession statement?

562
00:34:11,240 --> 00:34:12,960
Since this matter involves the Empress,

563
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:14,370
without your permission, Father,

564
00:34:14,370 --> 00:34:15,040
I

565
00:34:15,330 --> 00:34:16,530
dare not act on my own.

566
00:34:18,850 --> 00:34:20,290
Stop putting on

567
00:34:20,810 --> 00:34:22,070
that act in front of me.

568
00:34:23,650 --> 00:34:24,580
Convey my order:

569
00:34:24,889 --> 00:34:26,820
bring Wan Xi in for interrogation.

570
00:34:28,370 --> 00:34:29,889
As you command, Father.

571
00:34:45,130 --> 00:34:45,750
Wan Xi.

572
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:48,210
Yes, Your Majesty.

573
00:34:52,250 --> 00:34:54,250
I will take good care of your family.

574
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:57,290
Go with peace of mind.

575
00:34:57,290 --> 00:34:59,880
Thank you for your kindness, Your Majesty.

576
00:35:19,010 --> 00:35:20,750
[Prince Rui's Mansion]

577
00:35:19,770 --> 00:35:20,660
Sir, do you know

578
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:22,040
if there's anyone

579
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:23,040
in the Tianshu Camp

580
00:35:23,040 --> 00:35:25,170
who was promoted to officer
without military merit?

581
00:35:25,170 --> 00:35:28,080
Only the former training officer
of the Tianshu Camp,

582
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:29,740
Jiang Heying. A few years ago,

583
00:35:30,250 --> 00:35:32,650
he said he wanted to return home
to care for his elderly mother.

584
00:35:32,650 --> 00:35:34,170
Chief General appreciated
his filial piety,

585
00:35:34,170 --> 00:35:37,170
so he recommended him for the position of
Chief Commander in his hometown, Qianzhou.

586
00:35:37,170 --> 00:35:38,890
Why are you asking about this,
Young Marshal?

587
00:35:38,890 --> 00:35:40,960
Because the method used
to assassinate my Father

588
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:43,000
is consistent with
Tianshu Camp's techniques.

589
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:43,850
Only those involved in developing

590
00:35:43,850 --> 00:35:45,810
the Tianshu Camp's combat formations

591
00:35:45,810 --> 00:35:47,670
would know the critical details.

592
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:49,210
The soldiers of the Shuoxi Army

593
00:35:49,210 --> 00:35:51,210
all revere Chief General like a god.

594
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:53,690
How could they commit
such a treasonous act?

595
00:35:53,690 --> 00:35:55,960
I personally performed the autopsy
on Prince Rui.

596
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:58,120
The wounds on his body don't lie.

597
00:35:59,170 --> 00:36:00,220
Jiang Heying

598
00:36:00,370 --> 00:36:03,700
owes everything he has today
to Chief General's promotion.

599
00:36:04,250 --> 00:36:06,120
How could he dare to kill Chief General

600
00:36:06,120 --> 00:36:07,960
and turn against the Shuoxi Army?

601
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:10,890
What if there was someone with power
greater than Father

602
00:36:10,890 --> 00:36:12,220
who ordered him to do so?

603
00:36:13,210 --> 00:36:15,690
What if he believed that person
could protect him

604
00:36:15,690 --> 00:36:17,690
and offer him a better future?

605
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:22,890
Chief General already held
such high position and power.

606
00:36:22,890 --> 00:36:25,080
The only ones with greater power
than Chief General are...

607
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:25,890
His Majesty,

608
00:36:26,970 --> 00:36:28,230
or the future emperor.

609
00:36:28,770 --> 00:36:30,370
Young Marshal, are you referring to...

610
00:36:30,370 --> 00:36:31,370
The Crown Prince?

611
00:36:32,290 --> 00:36:34,670
The Empress's father and brothers
command the Northern Palace Army.

612
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:37,290
There's no need for them
to win over the Shuoxi Army as well.

613
00:36:37,290 --> 00:36:38,730
Besides, His Majesty has already
expressed dissatisfaction

614
00:36:38,730 --> 00:36:40,370
with the Crown Prince's obsession
with literature

615
00:36:40,370 --> 00:36:42,250
and lack of interest in state affairs.

616
00:36:42,250 --> 00:36:43,810
Everyone at court knows this.

617
00:36:43,810 --> 00:36:45,420
His Majesty's always turned a blind eye
to Prince Cheng's

618
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:47,000
open and covert suppression
of the Crown Prince.

619
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:49,770
If Jiang Heying wanted to earn merit
by supporting the future emperor,

620
00:36:49,770 --> 00:36:51,000
of course he would choose

621
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,400
the currently ascendant

622
00:36:52,520 --> 00:36:53,320
Prince Cheng.

623
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,730
So it's him.

624
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,170
Besides, Jiang Heying

625
00:36:57,170 --> 00:36:58,650
was deeply trusted by Father,

626
00:36:58,650 --> 00:37:00,400
and he knows
Father's fighting skills well.

627
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,710
He also knows the border patrol routes

628
00:37:01,710 --> 00:37:02,840
better than anyone.

629
00:37:03,330 --> 00:37:04,930
As well as your whereabouts.

630
00:37:05,170 --> 00:37:07,120
If Jiang Heying has been colluding with
Prince Cheng for long, then the mastermind

631
00:37:07,120 --> 00:37:09,440
behind the assassination attempt
on you and Father

632
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:11,500
was very likely Prince Cheng, Yan Qi.

633
00:37:12,150 --> 00:37:13,370
If it was Prince Cheng,

634
00:37:13,370 --> 00:37:15,300
we still have ways to deal with him.

635
00:37:15,330 --> 00:37:17,400
But if the one who ordered Jiang Heying

636
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,920
is His Majesty himself,

637
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:21,120
what should we do then?

638
00:37:21,120 --> 00:37:23,210
Whether it's His Majesty or Prince Cheng,

639
00:37:23,210 --> 00:37:24,870
we must proceed with caution.

640
00:37:25,210 --> 00:37:26,370
The top priority now

641
00:37:26,690 --> 00:37:29,250
is to protect the current strength
of the Shuoxi Army.

642
00:37:29,250 --> 00:37:30,850
I have to trouble you, Sir, to return
to Shuoxi

643
00:37:30,850 --> 00:37:31,920
and tell our men

644
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:32,920
to lie low for now,

645
00:37:33,040 --> 00:37:34,480
until I uncover the truth.

646
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:36,140
Then we'll plan our next move.

647
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:38,250
As you command, Young Marshal.

648
00:37:42,810 --> 00:37:44,890
This time,
we might be stirring up a hornet's nest.

649
00:37:44,890 --> 00:37:45,750
Are you afraid?

650
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:47,520
No.

651
00:37:50,250 --> 00:37:51,710
Master, Princess Yongci.

652
00:37:52,370 --> 00:37:55,480
His Majesty has ordered Prince Cheng
to interrogate Wan Xi from Fengyi Palace.

653
00:37:55,480 --> 00:37:57,040
Did the Empress not intervene?

654
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:57,690
No.

655
00:37:57,910 --> 00:37:59,440
This Wan Xi seemed prepared.

656
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:01,040
He went obediently with Prince Cheng.

657
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:02,890
How could someone as dominant
as the Empress

658
00:38:02,890 --> 00:38:05,350
allow Wan Xi to be taken away
by Prince Cheng?

659
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:07,170
She was just cutting her losses.

660
00:38:07,170 --> 00:38:08,370
I wasn't certain before

661
00:38:08,370 --> 00:38:09,810
whether Song Xiwen's death

662
00:38:09,810 --> 00:38:11,560
had anything to do with the Empress.

663
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:12,720
But now it seems

664
00:38:13,270 --> 00:38:14,600
it was indeed her doing.

665
00:38:14,810 --> 00:38:16,140
Wan Xi was so compliant,

666
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:18,600
as if he'd already resigned to his fate.

667
00:38:18,690 --> 00:38:19,850
This time, Prince Cheng

668
00:38:19,850 --> 00:38:21,780
will likely come up empty-handed.

669
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:55,140
Your Highness.

670
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:57,170
Attendant Wan is not a murder suspect.

671
00:38:57,170 --> 00:38:58,330
Such torture

672
00:38:58,330 --> 00:38:59,920
seems rather inappropriate.

673
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:01,520
If he had confessed earlier,

674
00:39:01,730 --> 00:39:04,060
he would have been spared such suffering,

675
00:39:04,730 --> 00:39:05,990
but he refuses to talk.

676
00:39:06,170 --> 00:39:08,290
But confessions obtained through torture

677
00:39:08,290 --> 00:39:10,150
are bound to contain falsehoods,

678
00:39:10,170 --> 00:39:12,210
and it violates the law as well.

679
00:39:12,210 --> 00:39:14,250
Prefect Zheng, you seem
to have forgotten that

680
00:39:14,250 --> 00:39:15,850
this is the Supreme Court,

681
00:39:16,250 --> 00:39:17,850
not the capital prefecture.

682
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:21,960
If you find this distasteful,
Prefect Zheng,

683
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:23,520
the exit is right over there.

684
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:24,370
Feel free to leave.

685
00:39:24,370 --> 00:39:24,960
Your Highness.

686
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:25,820
Your Highness.

687
00:39:26,040 --> 00:39:28,600
His Majesty ordered me and Prefect Zheng
to oversee the interrogation.

688
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:29,310
If he

689
00:39:29,560 --> 00:39:31,000
dies under torture,

690
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:33,190
and His Majesty inquires about it,

691
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:35,790
I'm afraid I would have to
report the truth.

692
00:39:39,890 --> 00:39:40,560
Your Highness.

693
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:41,750
Wan Xi's heart and lungs
are already damaged.

694
00:39:41,750 --> 00:39:43,500
I'm afraid he won't survive another round.

695
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:45,360
Send Wan Xi back to Fengyi Palace.

696
00:39:45,890 --> 00:39:46,960
Whether to save him or not

697
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,400
is entirely up to Her Majesty.

698
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,530
Yes, Your Highness.

699
00:39:51,130 --> 00:39:52,780
[Funing Palace]

700
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,370
Ze.

701
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:19,650
Please let my grandma win this time.

702
00:40:19,650 --> 00:40:20,650
If she loses,

703
00:40:20,720 --> 00:40:22,650
she'll make me practice Go
with her again.

704
00:40:22,650 --> 00:40:24,170
Don't you mock me.

705
00:40:24,170 --> 00:40:26,600
My Go skills
have improved greatly lately.

706
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:29,460
I've beaten His Majesty
three times in a row.

707
00:40:29,560 --> 00:40:30,890
I'm about to win this game.

708
00:40:30,890 --> 00:40:31,850
Grand Princess,

709
00:40:31,850 --> 00:40:33,370
you actually beat His Majesty?

710
00:40:33,370 --> 00:40:34,970
His Majesty is a master of Go.

711
00:40:35,170 --> 00:40:36,650
Before I went out to seek a doctor,

712
00:40:36,650 --> 00:40:37,960
I played Go with His Majesty

713
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:39,290
and never won even once.

714
00:40:40,170 --> 00:40:42,370
His Majesty is busy with court affairs.

715
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,940
Not to mention playing Go,

716
00:40:44,100 --> 00:40:45,110
he hasn't had

717
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:47,180
any leisure time these years.

718
00:40:49,210 --> 00:40:50,920
His Majesty is diligent in his governance.

719
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:52,250
It's truly exhausting.

720
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:54,120
Please.

721
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,380
Little Wan'er, come here.

722
00:40:57,920 --> 00:40:59,600
If my grandma wins this Go game,

723
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:01,200
she'll give us some rewards.

724
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:03,770
Greetings, Your Majesty.

725
00:41:03,770 --> 00:41:04,440
Grandma.

726
00:41:05,330 --> 00:41:06,860
Why are you here alone?

727
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,730
Didn't Chi come with you?

728
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:10,560
He...

729
00:41:11,470 --> 00:41:14,070
He asked me to come
check Your Majesty's pulse.

730
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:18,370
Chi is always so thoughtful.

731
00:41:18,980 --> 00:41:20,440
I'm feeling tired anyway.

732
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:21,810
You can continue

733
00:41:22,290 --> 00:41:23,770
this Go game another day.

734
00:41:24,250 --> 00:41:24,960
Indeed.

735
00:41:25,250 --> 00:41:27,170
We've been bothering you for too long.

736
00:41:27,170 --> 00:41:27,960
Wan.

737
00:41:27,960 --> 00:41:31,090
After checking her pulse,
let Sister-in-law rest well.

738
00:41:31,690 --> 00:41:32,790
Ning, let's go.

739
00:41:35,040 --> 00:41:36,450
See Grand Princess out.

740
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,250
Yes.

741
00:41:45,440 --> 00:41:46,290
What is it?

742
00:41:48,210 --> 00:41:49,410
Nothing too serious.

743
00:41:50,040 --> 00:41:53,040
It's just Yan Chi and I have
some questions about the Song Xiwen case,

744
00:41:53,040 --> 00:41:55,900
on which we would like your guidance,
Your Majesty.

745
00:42:01,290 --> 00:42:02,730
Song Xiwen?

746
00:42:03,040 --> 00:42:05,890
Is Song Xiwen that guard
from Prince Jin's residence?

747
00:42:05,890 --> 00:42:06,560
Yes.

748
00:42:06,990 --> 00:42:08,690
An attendant from
the Imperial Punishment Department

749
00:42:08,690 --> 00:42:10,650
confessed that it was Wan Xi,
the Empress's personal attendant,

750
00:42:10,650 --> 00:42:12,050
who took Song Xiwen away.

751
00:42:12,080 --> 00:42:13,520
Therefore, Prince Cheng arrested Wan Xi

752
00:42:13,520 --> 00:42:14,890
and tortured him severely,

753
00:42:14,890 --> 00:42:16,690
but he didn't confess anything.

754
00:42:17,020 --> 00:42:19,460
Wan Xi once served me in the palace.

755
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:22,680
He's extremely loyal,

756
00:42:22,850 --> 00:42:24,200
but also very stubborn.

757
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:26,170
If he doesn't want to talk,

758
00:42:26,170 --> 00:42:27,650
no one can make him.

759
00:42:27,850 --> 00:42:29,560
But there's no smoke without fire.

760
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:32,330
For this attendant
to specifically bring Wan Xi's name up,

761
00:42:32,330 --> 00:42:33,790
even if he said nothing,

762
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:35,690
there must be some connection.

763
00:42:36,170 --> 00:42:37,690
Since it involves Prince Jin,

764
00:42:37,690 --> 00:42:39,220
Yan Chi is quite concerned.

765
00:42:39,250 --> 00:42:41,560
Chi always refuses to believe

766
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:43,730
that Prince Jin would do such a thing.

767
00:42:43,850 --> 00:42:45,440
So he wants to find out

768
00:42:45,440 --> 00:42:47,370
what exactly happened that night.

769
00:42:47,890 --> 00:42:50,220
Prince Jin is a good boy
and a good brother.

770
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:53,090
Among all the princes,
he's closest to Chi.

771
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:55,400
Make sure to investigate this case
thoroughly,

772
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:57,920
so that we can give Prince Jin
an explanation.

773
00:42:57,920 --> 00:42:59,380
Whatever you want to know,

774
00:42:59,520 --> 00:43:00,980
I'll tell you everything.

775
00:43:02,960 --> 00:43:04,290
Years ago,

776
00:43:04,380 --> 00:43:06,610
I heard that Wan Xi adopted

777
00:43:06,630 --> 00:43:07,870
a godson

778
00:43:08,040 --> 00:43:09,330
named Wang Han in the Imperial Guard,

779
00:43:09,330 --> 00:43:10,960
who earned Wan Xi's complete trust.

780
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:11,670
Master.

781
00:43:11,920 --> 00:43:13,290
To catch this guy,

782
00:43:13,290 --> 00:43:14,960
it took several of our men to tie him up.

783
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:16,020
Who is your master?

784
00:43:16,920 --> 00:43:18,170
Who are you people?

785
00:43:19,790 --> 00:43:21,110
Why is he so terrified?

786
00:43:22,040 --> 00:43:23,300
I hear a woman's voice.

787
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:24,400
Are you from the palace?

788
00:43:24,400 --> 00:43:24,950
I...

789
00:43:25,170 --> 00:43:26,700
I won't betray Her Majesty!

790
00:43:27,410 --> 00:43:28,710
I don't want the money or

791
00:43:28,710 --> 00:43:30,960
my position in the Imperial Guard anymore!

792
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:31,960
Please, let me go!

793
00:43:31,960 --> 00:43:32,960
And let... Let...

794
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:34,770
Let my family go!

795
00:43:35,120 --> 00:43:36,400
Don't let him talk nonsense.

796
00:43:36,400 --> 00:43:37,960
Gag him and bury him now.

797
00:43:38,650 --> 00:43:39,210
Yes.

798
00:43:39,210 --> 00:43:40,920
No, please don't!

799
00:43:41,020 --> 00:43:41,700
I... I...

800
00:43:41,720 --> 00:43:43,780
Stop talking nonsense here. Shut up!

801
00:43:45,250 --> 00:43:46,380
Don't worry, Madam.

802
00:43:47,040 --> 00:43:48,590
Once this pit is dug,

803
00:43:48,810 --> 00:43:50,040
we'll make sure he dies

804
00:43:50,040 --> 00:43:51,400
without a sound.

805
00:43:52,960 --> 00:43:54,030
As you command.

806
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:02,210
You fool.

807
00:44:02,480 --> 00:44:04,580
Did you really think
you'd make it out alive?

808
00:44:04,580 --> 00:44:06,060
Her Majesty already said

809
00:44:06,170 --> 00:44:08,430
you shouldn't be left any way
to survive.

810
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:23,600
Don't run! Stop right there!

811
00:44:23,810 --> 00:44:24,810
Stop right there!

812
00:44:24,920 --> 00:44:25,600
Stop!

813
00:44:26,440 --> 00:44:27,170
Don't run!

814
00:44:35,650 --> 00:44:38,250
Help!
Someone's trying to kill and silence me!

815
00:44:38,460 --> 00:44:39,390
Help!

816
00:44:39,920 --> 00:44:41,560
Sir, please help me!

817
00:44:41,560 --> 00:44:42,480
Gentler, okay?

818
00:44:42,480 --> 00:44:44,730
Sir, they're trying to kill
and silence me!

819
00:44:44,730 --> 00:44:46,400
Help me, Sir!

